# Per-Dockerfile ignore for the e2e runner (BuildKit prefers this over the root
# .dockerignore). Same exclusions, EXCEPT we keep e2e/ - the runner needs the
# specs and support harness. Patterns are relative to the build context (repo root).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/.vite
.git
.github
**/*.log
